Tetraktys — the quaternary cardinal oscillator. An original toy model: the NSEW
spec, the engine (sim/nsew.py), the sigils/generators, the landing, and the DLW
tag. The mathematics and physics it embodies are credited to their discoverers
(see agents/tetraktys.spun); the emergence claims are scoped to what the engine
actually measures (see SPEC.md), and the cosmology is kept as visible mythology.

